ZH: 我曾经攀爬过许多高耸的山峰。
EN: I have climbed many towering peaks before.
ZH: 这座山峰被云雾所包围。
EN: This peak is shrouded in clouds and mist.
ZH: 艰难的登山之旅终于抵达了山峰。
EN: The challenging mountain climbing journey finally reached the peak.
ZH: 那座山峰高耸入云。
EN: That peak soars high into the clouds.
ZH: 山峰上积雪皑皑，风景如画。
EN: The peak is covered in glistening snow, creating a picturesque view.
ZH: 山峰的顶部被一片浓雾所遮盖。
EN: The top of the peak is veiled by dense fog.
ZH: 我们在山峰上搭起了帐篷。
EN: We set up our tents on the peak.
ZH: 这个国家的最高山峰是哪座？
EN: Which mountain is the highest peak in this country?
ZH: 从山峰上可以俯瞰整个城市的美景。
EN: The view of the entire city can be seen from the peak.
ZH: 那座山峰是我们明天的目标。
EN: That peak is our destination for tomorrow.
ZH: 山峰上的风景如诗如画。
EN: The scenery on the peak is like a painting.
ZH: 山峰是许多登山者的挑战。
EN: The peak is a challenge for many climbers.
ZH: 峭壁陡峭的山峰看起来令人望而却步。
EN: The steep cliffs of the peak look intimidating.
ZH: 他的目标是攀登世界各地的最高山峰。
EN: His goal is to climb the highest peaks around the world.
ZH: 这座山峰被誉为登山者的天堂。
EN: This peak is hailed as a paradise for climbers.
ZH: 山峰脚下是一片宁静的湖泊。
EN: At the foot of the peak lies a serene lake.
ZH: 冰川覆盖着那座山峰的顶部。
EN: The peak's summit is covered by glaciers.
ZH: 骏马犹如山峰一样挺拔高亢。
EN: The spirited horse stands tall and proud like a peak.
ZH: 他们决定挑战登顶那座险峻的山峰。
EN: They decided to take on the challenge of summiting that steep peak.
ZH: 每年都有许多人来登顶这座著名的山峰。
EN: Every year, many people come to summit this famous peak.
